    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are within scope of MRL 2 exemptions. CFD-predicted RH values satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five COU operating points, supported by comparison against the CPB clinical registry dataset. The assessment team notes that the registry-based validation evidence is extensive and clinically representative, providing high confidence in the model's predictive capability for the intended use.",
